# Optional: app-wide Google OAuth Client ID for one-tap Google Drive backup.
#
# When set, the History → "Cloud backup (Google Drive)" card shows Back up /
# Restore buttons that sign the user in with your app — no per-user setup. When
# unset, the card falls back to the bring-your-own-Client-ID flow.
#
# This value is PUBLIC (embedded in the client bundle). OAuth Client IDs are not
# secrets — do NOT put a client *secret* here (none is needed for this flow).
#
# How to obtain it — see the "Google Drive backup" section in README.md.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
